    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/5ae6e0f8ca9e8591e04057759f5e977d.webp?t=1743212745\" width=463 height=57 /></span><br><br>Plunder Islands is a fast paced arcade style game. You play Pirate Pete, who has to run, jump, and climb to beat each island. Your goal is to collect all the coins from each island then plunder the treasure chests.  No training mode needed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/8a78247c1924bbe67cdfb8be1907f14c.avif?t=1743212745\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/940cf078a9a696bd2e881f54c5736237.webp?t=1743212745\" width=463 height=57 /></span><br>Each island has its own unique challenges with no continues!  There are 20 islands plus bonus levels for extra lives.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/31117b7eafc2674a299f50dbbfc91ccd.avif?t=1743212745\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Play on keyboard or controller. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/b858077db4be5b21a41e4748fbfa4e15.webp?t=1743212745\" width=463 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/5a0d2e21332f2fba688d1d4cee52e73a.avif?t=1743212745\" width=160 height=129 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279370/extras/270b4be22d65a103ce020ffecf9cf088.avif?t=1743212745\" width=160 height=129 /><